eu.trentorise.opendata.traceprov.dcat

  • Packages that use eu.trentorise.opendata.traceprov.dcat 
    Package Description
    eu.trentorise.opendata.traceprov.dcat
    Package holds immutable models for DCAT.
  • Classes in eu.trentorise.opendata.traceprov.dcat used by eu.trentorise.opendata.traceprov.dcat 
    Class and Description
    AbstractFoafAgent
    Only used to generate a FoafAgent with builder.
    ADcatCatalog
    A data catalog is a curated collection of metadata about datasets, as specified by dcat:catalog Typically, a web-based data catalog is represented as a single instance of this class.
    ADcatCatalogRecord
    A record in a data catalog, describing a single dataset, as specified by dcat: CatalogRecorda This class is optional and not all catalogs will use it.
    ADcatDataset
    A collection of data, published or curated by a single agent, and available for access or download in one or more formats.
    ADcatDistribution
    Models a dcat: Distribution
    AFoafAgent
    Models a minimal FOAF Agent
